[0.0,"o","\r\nPipeline:\r\n  1. record (compile): record a fast terminal baseline and timeline sidecar\r\n"]
[0.0,"o","  2. audio_generate (compile): generate or reuse cached TTS fragments for each beat\r\n"]
[0.0,"o","  3. audio_publish (link): concatenate voiceover and write audio timing metadata\r\n  4. retime (optimize): create the watchable cast using terminal and audio timing\r\n"]
[0.0,"o","  5. publish_surface (link): embed the finished recording in the selected publish surface\r\n  6. align_check (validate): verify visible captions and commands still match the script\r\n\r\nNo commands were run.\r\n"]
